{"tid":1631910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[長文慎入]幾個月黎不分化既精神去晒邊","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:50:33.000Z","uid":125224,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8e55280bc7eb9566129ea12efa9bac10c73317","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"我地依家要做既係反思 改善 唔係指責同責怪<br />\n和勇和勇 不嬲都係成一體 分化撚係咁係到叫其中一方退場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場運動一直以黎就係雙方合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔應該再叫任何一方退場<br />\n運動入面有狗不嬲大家都知道 任何post 不論佢論點係唔係成立都好 唔該大家用好d既語氣去建立討論風氣 唔係一黎就和理非或者勇武其中一方好似錯撚曬咁 內容又只有破壞 毫無建設<br />\n聽日<br />\n依家應該要做既係<br />\n1. 文宣 向外國解釋點解我地會以暴制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />並唔係因為大家持相反意見  <br />\n另外係區內文宣都要做多d 痴連儂牆 始終唔係好多人跟得咁貼 特別係睇完張相見到人爆曬血 但又無睇曬全篇報導了解真相既人 區內文宣都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n的士撞人 黑警私刑 軍營有防暴 單單都要講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 好多人上連登都係有時間追熱門 唔希望下到黎只係見到大家互相指責 同咁多分化撚post 希望大家理性d 見到任何指責勇武或者和理非既post 回應前諗一諗 個post係咪只係有破壞無建設 係咪應該有更加好既討論風氣去解決問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不分化 不割蓆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明白大家見到手足比人拉同打好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都唔好意氣用事令成個連登只係有指責既風氣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">單純叫一方退場真係解決問題既方法?</span><br />\n3. 推返多d行動post或者討論出黎 近呢一兩次活動因為好急 所以有d詳情無一個共識 (到底點解一開始只係講港島 最後多個條九龍線 九龍線又點解有人話深水埗終點 又有人話係九龍塘 去到今朝先有人發現深水埗條路線好多狗屋?) 依家已經無從考究 但帶出既係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地要更多討論post去訂立一個確定既地點去開花/遊行</span> 討論個陣大家都要明白對方既論點去商議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 勇武裝修其實好需要和理非幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不論係事前工作 了解唔同商鋪背景以免犯錯定係現場只係開遮 都好重要 和理非應該踏出一步 去開遮幫下手 唔好只係再企係隔離只係望啦<br />\n勇武係行動之前都記住唔好衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用火魔法前考慮環境適唔適合 會唔會影響民居 叫神獸之前記得FC左先 以免犯錯 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算大家做錯d乜 核彈都唔割 互補不足 好唔好?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自蒙面法之後既行動都欠缺足夠既時間去討論 所以大家更加要推多d行動post <br />\n香港人 反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae9c0cbe2d25f76e80fa5b8e375e70fe66a8316","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a072da61f287e27bb80341083ef5a31328a2e68","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf1b31cd4050a0d826dfda1c6fbedc5f9cf04c8","tid":1631910,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"7ef49a2c4c1ca712f248200e7e611ab3c546e200","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"自推3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0b06ff3be538b8deefa1b0fe91d5fdfd905a7b","tid":1631910,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1500df74f576ed04b7e9f9d8efd9c29c511381f","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e62a0f971bddfd42f57b2ebb678b7128947545","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d48756a808757b6d9950946c52cd5047febf8fe","tid":1631910,"uid":290896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"推唔郁"},{"pid":"9e0d61f560bc4fa018fbd8b93d275fcd04c3b801","tid":1631910,"uid":23400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"手足私了左馬碲露可能會出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629792</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n連登幾撚時變到咁撚極端咁撚唔聽意見？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629578</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我單打獨鬥屌佢老母，真係好易睇得出分化撚"},{"pid":"2e87595560b7b7cc4718cf08d2bd149a53ccaf21","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7cb35c9b87bbab4ca5b736c27006c9e5c406ff","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed429a01679cf0e5a3bc7feec772531a87833020","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6094fd7f0fa33a8054227cfc5a67fa0befd330","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6882dbe07d2e853e09735c06c1bc931d04418e3","tid":1631910,"uid":257974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"當連登成為抗爭者主要平台，難免有班人出黎分化。<br />\n外部就ddos等你上唔到，內部就入黎放流料玩風向。<br />\n<br />\n自己小心分析好過"},{"pid":"4cd246fd5901a76bdc724adee65216409d901e1e","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da62728015389759b157c1e068c2c6371e9433a","tid":1631910,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6882dbe07d2e853e09735c06c1bc931d04418e3","tid":1631910,"uid":257974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"當連登成為抗爭者主要平台，難免有班人出黎分化。<br />\n外部就ddos等你上唔到，內部就入黎放流料玩風向。<br />\n<br />\n自己小心分析好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"唔好再比人帶風向去分化自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d4c077b209f4ccde21b140fb553185e0251bdb","tid":1631910,"uid":278399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要記返起6月嗰陣我地不斷提及香港人嘅特性就係聰明，靈活，識變通<br />\n可以唔硬碰就唔硬碰，可以智取就智取啦<br />\n啲力水留返嚟必要時打怪<br />\n唔洗浪費太多精力喺嘍囉身上㗎"},{"pid":"4ed36a4bf962bfcf4e77e9823263416dde9de669","tid":1631910,"uid":278399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf1b31cd4050a0d826dfda1c6fbedc5f9cf04c8","tid":1631910,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:31.000Z","msg"